description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 3 of 4 of the live November match up between Team Ice and The Goddesses.
The energy of the live audience picks up and the wrestlers feel the energy. All four girls bring it to the final round, no one wants to lose. The losers get fucked and humiliated in front of the live crowd and no one wants that. This round has amazing scissor holds, brutal full nelsons, and plenty of 2 on 1 action, as girls who are helpless on the mat also get fingered and penetrated. This was one of the most intense rounds we have seen in Tag Team Action!
title: 4 girls going head to head in unscripted live wrestling in front of a live audience
